BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 720.0 Td (3. APPROVAL QUEUE MANAGEMENT) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 704.0 Td (Approvals pending in the queue for more than 8 business hours are automatically) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 688.0 Td (escalated to the next management level. The operations team must review the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 672.0 Td (approval queue dashboard at the start of each business day.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 648.0 Td (4. THRESHOLDS REFERENCE \(as of SOP effective date\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 632.0 Td (The following thresholds apply to standard catalogue materials:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 616.0 Td (- Below $5,000 with preferred vendor: auto-approved) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 600.0 Td (- $5,000 to $25,000: manager approval required) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 584.0 Td (- Above $25,000: executive approval required \(system denies and routes to CapEx) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 568.0 Td (board\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 544.0 Td (These values are governed by POL-PROC-001. If POL-PROC-001 is updated, this SOP) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 528.0 Td (reference table must be updated in the same change cycle.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 504.0 Td (5. EXCEPTION HANDLING) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 488.0 Td (If the policy evaluation engine cannot extract a numeric threshold from a policy) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 472.0 Td (document \(ambiguous language\), it defaults to routing the requisition for human) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 456.0 Td (review. Operations staff should log such exceptions and notify the compliance) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 440.0 Td (team to update the policy wording.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 416.0 Td (6. AUDIT TRAIL) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 400.0 Td (Every automated procurement decision produces a machine-readable audit record) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 384.0 Td (containing: material ID, vendor ID, estimated cost, the policy rule that fired,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 368.0 Td (the outcome, and a timestamp. These records are retained in the Cosmos DB audit) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 352.0 Td (container for a minimum of 7 years in accordance with the company records) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 336.0 Td (retention policy.) Tj ET
endstream
